{"tid":1238225,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"知識分享:   差餉 =「差人」的糧餉","createTime":"2019-06-17T17:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T17:39:09.000Z","uid":73407,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d0a655ea05d93e81f62e9bbaaf09294032dfee8b","tid":1238225,"uid":73407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:39:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/theme/rates/duk/origin-of-rating.shtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.1823.gov.hk%2Fbig5%2Ftheme%2Frates%2Fduk%2Forigin-of-rating.shtm&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXnIsb0SIwbGp5IKHDv9YBGc%3D&h=8ee25acb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/theme/rates/duk/origin-of-rating.shtm</a><br />\n<br />\n差餉 =「差人」的糧餉？<br />\n<br />\n沒錯！第一條《差餉條例》（1845 年第 2 號條例）在 1845 年生效時，的確是為了支付維持香港警隊所需的開支。當時，該稅項稱為「差役餉項」，說明了徵收這稅項的原意，現時則已改稱為「差餉」。隨著公共設施和服務日漸完善，差餉收入也用來支付公共照明系統、食水及消防等服務的開支。"}]}